    <main class="main-panel">
      <div class="page-header-area">
        <h1 class="page-title">Date Picker</h1>
        <p class="page-desc">A date input that triggers a calendar popover for selecting a single date or date range. Supports direct keyboard entry (DD/MM/YYYY), preset shortcuts, optional Apply / Cancel / Clear footer, min / max bounds, and RTL layouts.</p>
        <nav class="content-tabs">
          <button class="tab-item active">Overview</button>
          <button class="tab-item">Style</button>
          <button class="tab-item">Usage</button>
          <button class="tab-item">Code</button>
          <button class="tab-item">Accessibility</button>
        </nav>
      </div>

      <div class="main-content-area">
        <div class="main-content-inner">

        <!-- ========== OVERVIEW ========== -->
        <div class="tab-content" id="tab-overview">
          <h3 id="anatomy" class="doc-h3">Anatomy</h3>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle" style="margin-bottom:28px;">The date picker popover is composed of four numbered regions. Each label is anchored to the live preview with a connector line.</p>
          <div class="anatomy-diagram" style="overflow:visible;">
            <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;padding:40px 0;">
              <div class="dp-wrapper" style="position:relative;">
                <!-- 1 Container: marker left of input -->
                <div style="position:absolute;right:calc(100% + 6px);top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;z-index:20;"><span class="anat-marker-inline">1</span><div style="width:28px;height:2px;background:#2563eb;"></div></div>
                <!-- 2 Calendar icon: marker above, vertical line down -->
                <div style="position:absolute;left:20px;bottom:calc(100% + 6px);transform:translateX(-50%);display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:4px;z-index:20;"><span class="anat-marker-inline">2</span><div style="width:2px;height:14px;background:#2563eb;"></div></div>
                <!-- 3 Placeholder / input: marker right of input -->
                <div style="position:absolute;left:calc(100% + 6px);top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);display:flex;flex-direction:row-reverse;align-items:center;gap:6px;z-index:20;"><span class="anat-marker-inline">3</span><div style="width:28px;height:2px;background:#2563eb;"></div></div>
                <div class="dp-input-field" data-dp-toggle="">
                  <span class="dp-cal-icon">
                    <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"></rect><path d="M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18"></path></svg>
                  </span>
                  <input class="dp-input" type="text" placeholder="DD/MM/YYYY" readonly="" value="">
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="anat-legend">
            <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">1</span><div><strong>Input Container</strong><span>Wrapper with border, radius, and focus ring. Holds the icon and input. Reacts to hover, focus, error, and disabled states.</span></div></div>
            <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">2</span><div><strong>Calendar Icon</strong><span>Leading affordance indicating the field opens a date picker. Clicking the icon toggles the popover.</span></div></div>
            <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">3</span><div><strong>Input</strong><span>Read-only text input displaying the selected date in <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);">DD/MM/YYYY</code> format. Falls back to placeholder when empty.</span></div></div>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div style="margin-bottom:64px;">
            <h2 id="live-demo" class="doc-section-title" style="margin-bottom:8px;">Preview</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle" style="margin-bottom:28px;">Click an input to open the calendar. Use navigation arrows to change month; click a day to select it.</p>
            <div class="demo-container">
              <div class="demo-toolbar"><div class="demo-theme-pill">Interactive preview</div></div>
              <div class="demo-canvas" style="align-items:flex-start;gap:48px;padding:48px 64px;flex-direction:row;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;">
                <!-- Single -->
                <div>
                  <span class="dp-label">Single</span>
                  <div id="demo-single" class="dp-wrapper" style="margin-top:6px;"></div>
                </div>
                <!-- Range -->
                <div>
                  <span class="dp-label">Range</span>
                  <div id="demo-range" class="dp-wrapper" style="margin-top:6px;"></div>
                </div>
                <!-- With Presets -->
                <div>
                  <span class="dp-label">With presets</span>
                  <div id="demo-presets" class="dp-wrapper" style="margin-top:6px;"></div>
                </div>
                <!-- With Footer -->
                <div>
                  <span class="dp-label">With footer</span>
                  <div id="demo-footer" class="dp-wrapper" style="margin-top:6px;"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="content-guidelines" class="doc-h3">Content Guidelines<span class="h3-badge" style="background:rgba(37,99,235,0.1);color:var(--prism-violet);">Recommended</span></h3>
            <div class="do-dont-grid">
              <div class="do-card"><span class="card-label">Do</span><ul>
                <li>Use <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">type="range"</code> when start and end dates are both required.</li>
                <li>Surface common spans as presets (Today, Last 7 / 30 days, This month).</li>
                <li>Enable <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">showFooter</code> when the picker drives an expensive operation.</li>
                <li>Respect <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">minDate</code> / <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">maxDate</code> &mdash; disable invalid days in the grid.</li>
                <li>Announce the selected date via <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">aria-live</code> on selection.</li>
                <li>Close the popover after Apply (or after single-click selection when no Footer).</li>
              </ul></div>
              <div class="dont-card"><span class="card-label">Don't</span><ul>
                <li>Use two independent Single pickers for a date range &mdash; they can't enforce end &ge; start.</li>
                <li>Hide presets behind "Custom" when &ge; 60% of users pick one of them.</li>
                <li>Enable Footer for inline form fields where immediate commit is expected.</li>
                <li>Let users pick an invalid date and only reject it on form submit.</li>
                <li>Flip only the input without mirroring the calendar grid in RTL.</li>
                <li>Hard-code one date format globally &mdash; keep it locale-aware.</li>
              </ul></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ========== STYLE ========== -->
        <div class="tab-content" id="tab-style" style="display:none;padding-top:32px;">
          <h2 id="style-overview" class="doc-section-title">Style</h2>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Design tokens, variants, and visual specifications that define the Date Picker's appearance.</p>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="variants" class="doc-section-title">Variants</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">2 Type &times; 2 State = 4 core variants. Runtime toggles (Show Presets, Show Footer, validation) multiply usage surfaces.</p>
            <table class="size-table">
              <thead><tr><th>Axis</th><th>Values</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td><strong>Type</strong></td><td><code>Single</code>, <code>Range</code></td><td>Single = one input + one calendar. Range = two inputs + dual calendar.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>State</strong></td><td><code>Closed</code>, <code>Open</code></td><td>Closed only renders the input(s); Open mounts the popover.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Show Presets</strong></td><td><code>false</code>, <code>true</code></td><td>Toggles the quick-select shortcuts column.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Show Footer</strong></td><td><code>false</code>, <code>true</code></td><td>Toggles the Clear / Cancel / Apply action row.</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>

            <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px;margin-top:28px;">
              <div style="padding:24px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:14px;">
                <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-bottom:12px;">Single</div>
                <div class="dp-input-field"><svg class="dp-cal-icon" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18"/></svg><input class="dp-input" readonly value="15/03/2026"></div>
                <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:10px;">One input, one calendar.</div>
              </div>
              <div style="padding:24px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:14px;">
                <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-bottom:12px;">Range</div>
                <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;">
                  <div class="dp-input-field" style="flex:1;"><svg class="dp-cal-icon" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18"/></svg><input class="dp-input" readonly value="01/03/2026"></div>
                  <div class="dp-input-field" style="flex:1;"><svg class="dp-cal-icon" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18"/></svg><input class="dp-input" readonly value="15/03/2026"></div>
                </div>
                <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:10px;">Two inputs + dual calendar panel.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="input-states" class="doc-section-title">Input States</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Six interaction / validation states driving border, shadow, and opacity.</p>
            <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:16px;margin-top:24px;">
              <div style="padding:20px;border-radius:14px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);text-align:center;">
                <div class="dp-input-field" style="width:100%;margin-bottom:12px;"><svg class="dp-cal-icon" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18"/></svg><input class="dp-input" readonly placeholder="DD/MM/YYYY"></div>
                <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);">Default</div>
              </div>
              <div style="padding:20px;border-radius:14px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);text-align:center;">
                <div class="dp-input-field" style="width:100%;margin-bottom:12px;border-color:var(--prism-text-muted);"><svg class="dp-cal-icon" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18"/></svg><input class="dp-input" readonly placeholder="DD/MM/YYYY"></div>
                <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);">Hover</div>
              </div>
              <div style="padding:20px;border-radius:14px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);text-align:center;">
                <div class="dp-input-field focused" style="width:100%;margin-bottom:12px;"><svg class="dp-cal-icon" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18"/></svg><input class="dp-input" readonly placeholder="DD/MM/YYYY"></div>
                <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);">Focus</div>
              </div>
              <div style="padding:20px;border-radius:14px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);text-align:center;">
                <div class="dp-input-field" style="width:100%;margin-bottom:12px;"><svg class="dp-cal-icon" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18"/></svg><input class="dp-input" readonly value="15/03/2026"></div>
                <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);">Filled</div>
              </div>
              <div style="padding:20px;border-radius:14px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);text-align:center;">
                <div class="dp-input-field error" style="width:100%;margin-bottom:12px;"><svg class="dp-cal-icon" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18"/></svg><input class="dp-input" readonly value="32/13/2026"></div>
                <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);">Error</div>
              </div>
              <div style="padding:20px;border-radius:14px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);text-align:center;">
                <div class="dp-input-field disabled" style="width:100%;margin-bottom:12px;"><svg class="dp-cal-icon" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18"/></svg><input class="dp-input" readonly placeholder="DD/MM/YYYY" disabled></div>
                <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);">Disabled</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="calendar-popover" class="doc-section-title">Calendar Popover</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">The popover surface that anchors 8px below the input. BG-Primary-alt, 8px radius, 1px border, Shadow-Medium.</p>
            <table class="size-table">
              <thead><tr><th>Property</th><th>Value</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td><strong>Popover width (single month)</strong></td><td>280 px</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Popover width (dual month)</strong></td><td>568 px (2 &times; 280px + 8px internal gap)</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Popover corner radius</strong></td><td>8 px (<code>radius-8</code>)</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Popover offset from input</strong></td><td>8 px (below)</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Internal padding</strong></td><td>12 px (<code>spacing/12</code>)</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Day cell size</strong></td><td>32 &times; 32 px</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Selected-day pill / circle</strong></td><td>28 &times; 28 px centred inside cell</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Preset column width</strong></td><td>160 px</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Footer height</strong></td><td>48 px</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Input width</strong></td><td>240 px (Single); 2 &times; 240 px + 8 px gap (Range)</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Input height</strong></td><td>32 px</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Input corner radius</strong></td><td>6 px (<code>radius-6</code>)</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Default border stroke</strong></td><td>1 px</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Focus border stroke</strong></td><td>2 px</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="color-tokens" class="doc-h3">Colour Tokens<span class="h3-badge" style="background:rgba(37,99,235,0.1);color:var(--prism-violet);">Tokens</span></h3>
            <table class="size-table">
              <thead><tr><th>Token</th><th>Role</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td><code>Background/BG-Primary-alt</code></td><td>Input background; popover background</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Background/BG-Accent</code></td><td>Selected day fill (Single); range endpoints (Range)</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Background/BG-Accent-Subtle</code></td><td>Days between range endpoints</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Background/BG-Hover</code></td><td>Day cell hover</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Background/BG-Disabled</code></td><td>Disabled input background</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Border/Border-Secondary</code></td><td>Input default border; popover border</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Border/Border-Accent</code></td><td>Focused input border (2 px)</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Border/Border-Error</code></td><td>Error input border</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Text/Text-Primary</code></td><td>Input value, current-month day numbers, header title</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Text/Text-Placeholder</code></td><td>Input placeholder (DD/MM/YYYY)</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Text/Text-Tertiary</code></td><td>Weekday-row abbreviations; helper text</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Text/Text-Disabled</code></td><td>Outside-month days; disabled days (min/max/disabledDates)</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Text/Text-Inverse</code></td><td>Day number on a selected cell (on BG-Accent)</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Text/Text-Link</code></td><td>Header chevrons + month-year label (clickable)</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Text/Text-Error</code></td><td>Required *; error helper text</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Shadow/Shadow-Medium</code></td><td>Popover drop shadow</td></tr>
